GYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDxAFnTI6ulI/v4/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;海湾战争让全球最大的移民走廊之一成为人们关注的焦点，数十亿美元的汇款面临风险，并考验着依赖外国工人维持海湾经济运行的经济模式。有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/LmYRfIw37b5ErXnjOYAFc4X7ert-uHiUgR440VvcYfXaklbWyOp-Q16icL4h7mhMlFL08nGbk892Pv-QBbRgAoNQIA3EdvEyW60fzQcbXZkj4i_suV6jc0jdmSM7zegowYBQUUFaAZS-wJCqV8CHcTaMMrNPG-3A9s9ROgG5Bcw0YMnSPolKSiTOcSFz7tz8MOXmaY1QeYWZai_uiBagHyu-K0J6wKglOqSF1amxTc6DDfOBJHJEaoC1YPUlWqoMQDmjf9TGPQhn-xKhsZgvbrORf5MAR3jxSsVIZ7FcyKKxdlh_zbBxWRMTHw4R8TKqsQJVcXpX5K_jQ92diqbVh58GD41TfiHqsF5ylUvXOWRSHK6kiVxSeS_68t1zpxOiCgITvUjocM1IPjuKn5RP6StSAPp2ZBxU9-b04p511vvBuUSNICrCJpX0kPCkkwGXFfqsdK3LQXBU6lQ4suAhSeaOqfKdUVVib0PGM4QrN-2oZBDFYRhwWU8fZ2lxdrsc0N2kxg5LyA5KgAOv7dSEZFoTly1V2_cvAHLZRH4tww/ozElWAv3bkvK6s7Kg5F3EHaWrt9kDI8a/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争使 1240 亿美元的海湾汇款生命线面临风险"&gt;明显的迹象表明，经济紧张&lt;/a&gt;，一些工人动用储蓄来维持汇款水平，如果冲突持续下去，可能会导致汇款总额急剧下降。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;数千名马拉维移民在德班一座清真寺外的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8-H0z2lDC-TvHVH5gCeWZ5sY9xv3bK7Y4A-avR52TplBeuBJF3zhUpLsVRjri8Fr99wEHGzyci9g03YtG8ViaaU44vg9qEI7fYn0yypYpvQ99wqQ4BiAJOZ50FCjVymVnBAcgnr4PPuPE719_Wwx-L4PsbOUnUqXTx86ybSORcA4QMg9-jrG5RvruPsJUbacKHeEibqGSre4zbENPRKYzZTIs4V6M0av2tVymGCPP80wg5Q_JOSoJIeD2OQmPxmPercrtJQ6VB5lpUDgCmP-3xuyH944dbWPu0Sio2BCeXcQeHnLFp3zGv4q0cUbGsELy0L5a-UqPwlosogTWskB_huxiG5CUHWrA2H7yS8hoDW1aLi_92OwM